Matte lipstick creates a silky texture on your lips. With its long wear performance, creamy texture, and oils in its formula, Silk Matte Liquid Lipstick protects your lips from drying.


Bringing velvety effect, perfect beauty and care together in a single product, Flormar lipstick will be indispensable for you

description_en:
Product Description:

The Cream21 Cream Orange L 250 ml is a perfect moisturizing lotion for your skin that can help you tackle all your skincare hassles. It is important that you understand the type of skin you have so that the product works effortlessly. This moisturizing lotion is mostly for dry skin, as it helps in boosting the skin and waking it up from its dryness.

Both men and women can use this lotion, and it can easily be applied to your hands and legs. This product comes as an all-in-one product that will help in moisturizing your skin and make it glow. It has a soothing consistency that does not take much time to dry up and starts working its magic instantly.

It can be used by both men and women. Perfect for dry skin conditions.

Helps in rejuvenating the skin with its composition, mostly for dry and patchy skin.
Perfect for daily care.
Incredible moisturizing abilities.
The lotion gets deeply soaked into the skin cuticles and thus helps in reviving the underlying dryness.
Provides a healthy glow to the skin.
Removes dead cells by getting absorbed deep into the skin.
Ensures deep nourishment.




How to use:

Take a generous amount of the lotion in your hand.

Mix it up a bit by rubbing it between your fingers, so that it spreads evenly when you apply it on your skin.
Spread it across your body evenly.
Massage thoroughly through the entire stretch of your hands and feet.
Let the lotion get soaked into your skin cuticles.
Let the lotion dry up completely as it gets absorbed into your skin.
After a while, rinse it off with warm water.
It is important that you wash off the moisturizer after it gets absorbed. Otherwise, it might have a reversed effect.
It is a bit different from other moisturizers that can be kept overnight; this needs to be washed off.




Caution & Warnings:




Keep it out of reach of children.
The composition of the lotion might not be suitable for all skin types, so it is important that you know what is suitable for your skin.
Children have much more sensitive and softer skin, so it might not be suitable for them.




Product Details:

Product Form: Cream
Quantity: 1 Pc
Brand: Cream 21

بالكامل.

امتصَّته بالكامل.

·  من المهم غسل المرطب بعد امتصاصه. وإلا

title_en: Kotex Mom Post Birth Pants L/Xl 8 Pieces
title_ar: كوتكس فوط داخلية للأم ما بعد الولادة كبير وكبير جدا 8 قطع
description_en:
Product Description:





ABSORBS 10X MORE for SUPERIOR PROTECTION: Kotex Mom Post Birth Disposable Underwear Pants absorb 10x more than a regular pad, providing superior protection against postpartum bleeding, so you can cherish worry-free moments with your baby.


FOR THE FIRST 10 DAYS POST BIRTH: Kotex post-birth pants are designed to play an important role in your postpartum recovery, helping you manage postpartum bleeding for the first 10 days after birth.


UNMATCHED COMFY MATERIAL: Made from super stretchable, breathable and soft materials, these post-birth pants comfortably fit your postpartum tummy – suitable for C-section too as it offers stretchy, breathable and soft waist band.


LONG BUILT-IN PAD: These pants features 40+cm long pad, to offers unmatched coverage and protection against discharge and leaks.


ACCOMMODATES BOTH LARGE & EXTRA-LARGE SIZES: Keeping your comfort in mind, Kotex Mom Post Birth Disposable Underwear has been designed with flexible materials to suit both large and extra-large sizes.



Product Details:

Product Type: Pads
Brand: Kotex
Product Form: Pants
description_ar:
وصف المنتج:





يمتص 10 أضعاف أكثر لحماية فائقة: سروال كوتكس للام بعد الولادة يمتص 10 أضعاف أكثر من الفوطة العادية، مما يوفر حماية فائقة ضد نزيف ما بعد الولادة، حتى تتمكني من الاستمتاع بلحظات خالية من القلق مع طفلك.


لأول 10 أيام بعد الولادة: صُمم سروال كوتكس لما بعد الولادة ليلعب دورًا مهمًا في تعافيك بعد الولادة، مما يساعدك على التحكم في نزيف ما بعد الولادة في الأيام العشرة الأولى بعد الولادة.


خامة مريحة لا مثيل لها: مصنوع من خامات فائقة التمدد والتهوية والنعومة، يناسب بنطال ما بعد الولادة بشكل مريح بطنك بعد الولادة - مناسب للولادة القيصرية أيضًا حيث يوفر حزام خصر قابل للتمدد والتهوية والنعومة.


وسادة طويلة مدمجة: يتميز هذا السروال بوسادة طويلة بطول 40 سم، لتوفير تغطية وحماية لا مثيل لها من الإفرازات والتسريبات.


يستوعب المقاسات الكبيرة والكبيرة جدًا: مع وضع راحتك في الاعتبار، صُممت الملابس الداخلية التي تستخدم لمرة واحدة بعد الولادة من كوتكس ماما، وهي مصممة بمواد مرنة لتناسب المقاسات الكبيرة والكبيرة جدًا.

description_en:
Product Description:





Effectively targets acne and blemishes at the source


What it is: A spot treatment which adheres to growing acne to effectively and quickly overcome areas of concern.





Product Features:





CentellAC-Rx Complex:





This formula not only treats acne but also helps revitalize and recover the skin without any irritation through COSRX Centella AC-Rx Complex. The calming formula includes three legendary healing ingredients--Madecassic acid, Asiaticoside, and Asiatic acid.





Overnight Magic for Visible Acne:





This formula gently and effectively dries out visible acne overnight using a skin-recovery complex that blends Zinc Oxide, Calamine, CentellAC-RX Complex




and Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Water.





Dual Block System:





New type of container that completely blocks air until you directly open for hygienic use.




How to use:





Squeeze the tube to use.


Apply an appropriate amount to the affected.





Caution & Warnings:





In case of allergy to any of the ingredients.





Ingredients:





Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Water, Butylene Glycol, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Glycerine, Zinc Oxide, Cetearyl Alcohol, Dimethyl Sulfone, Betaine, Polysorbate 60, Elaeis Guineensis (Palm) Oil, Elaeis Guineensis (Palm) Kernel Oil, Cetearyl Olivate, Sorbitan Olivate, 1,2-Hexanediol, Calamine, Dimethicone, Illicium Verum (Anise) Fruit Extract, Scutellaria Baicalensis Root Extract, Xanthan gum, Melaleuca Alternifolia (Tea Tree) Leaf Oil, Ethyl Hexanediol, Asiaticoside, Asiatic acid, Madecassic acid
